 The nominations for the 22nd Vodafone Ghana Music Awards (VGMA 2021) have been revealed. The award recognizes and celebrates the hard work and dedication of various stakeholders and players in the music industry. This year’s edition celebrates more than two decades of honouring worthy creatives in Ghana and Africa at large. See the list of the nominees below: Gospel Song of the Year Blessed – Akesse Brempong ft. Joe Mettle
Favour Everywhere – Celestine ft. Evelyn Wanjiru
